<inglise> (c) contracts of suretyship granted and on collateral securities furnished by persons acting for purposes outside their trade, business or profession; </inglise>
<eesti> c) k&auml;enduslepingud, milles tagatise andjaks on v&auml;ljaspool oma ametit, &auml;ri v&otilde;i elukutset tegutsevad isikud; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) contracts governed by family law or by the law of succession. </inglise>
