<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where an information society service is provided that consists of the storage of information provided by a recipient of the service, Member States shall ensure that the service provider is not liable for the information stored at the request of a recipient of the service, on condition that: </inglise>
