<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> This Article shall not affect the possibility for a court or administrative authority, in accordance with Member States' legal systems, of requiring the service provider to terminate or prevent an infringement, nor does it affect the possibility for Member States of establishing procedures governing the removal or disabling of access to information. </inglise>
