<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall encourage bodies responsible for the out-of-court settlement of, in particular, consumer disputes to operate in a way which provides adequate procedural guarantees for the parties concerned. </inglise>
